DAY-7

Aaj ka kaam (Quiz System & Assessment Logic)

1) Quiz Controller & Service Implementation
- QuizController me comprehensive quiz management:
  - POST /api/quizzes → create quiz with questions JSON
  - GET /api/quizzes → list all quizzes
  - GET /api/quizzes/{id} → get quiz details
  - PUT /api/quizzes/{id} → update quiz
  - DELETE /api/quizzes/{id} → remove quiz
  - PATCH /api/quizzes/{id}/active → toggle active status

2) Quiz Generation Logic
- Auto quiz generation feature add kiya:
  - POST /api/quizzes/generate?topicId=1&difficulty=MEDIUM
  - Topic aur difficulty ke basis pe questions generate karta hai
  - JSON format me questions structure with options aur correct answers

3) Quiz Submission & Evaluation
- Quiz attempt aur scoring system:
  - POST /api/quizzes/{id}/submit → submit answers
  - Real-time evaluation with score calculation
  - Detailed results with correct/incorrect breakdown
  - Performance metrics generation

4) Quiz Filtering & Search
- Advanced filtering options:
  - GET /api/quizzes/topic/{topicId} → topic-wise quizzes
  - GET /api/quizzes/difficulty/{difficulty} → difficulty-wise filter
  - GET /api/quizzes/language/{language} → language-based search

5) Questions JSON Structure Standardization
- Consistent format for storing quiz questions:
  ```json
  {
    "questions": [
      {
        "question": "What is Spring Boot?",
        "options": ["Framework", "Language", "Database"],
        "correct": 0
      }
    ]
  }
  ```

Testing Done
- Quiz creation with multiple questions working.
- Answer submission and scoring functional.
- Quiz filtering by various parameters successful.

Next Steps (DAY-8)
- UserProgress tracking system implement karna hai.
- Learning analytics aur metrics add karna hai.
- Performance optimization karna hai.

